 Front Cover <http://bookshop.informamedia.com/emails/nmm/cover.gif>As an industry professional you have been specially selected to receive three FREE issues of New Media Markets, the weekly newsletter providing expert analysis, industry data and market news on the converging media industry. 

Now in its 19th year of publication, New Media Markets covers all the essential market trends and regularly features news, analysis and data on: 

* cable, satellite and digital-terrestrial TV
* pay-TV, pay-per-view and video-on-demand
* interactive television and t-commerce
* new television technology
* programming
* regulation
* IPOs, bond issues and other financial deals. 

One week is a long time in the fast-paced world of the modern media industry. Timely, accurate information is the key to success. For a fraction of the cost of employing an external consultant or undertaking your own market research, New Media Markets brings you: 

* hard news on the European media industry 
* analysis of financing deals, franchising agreements and joint ventures 
* detailed insight into regulatory changes 
* the latest data on audience research, BARB viewing figures and international surveys 
* discussion of market strategies and financial performance. 

	
"Essential time-sensitive reading material for us in the financial markets"
Neil Blackley, European Media Analyst, Merrill Lynch. 	


